PrecisAppointment of CALVIN H. BUSS, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Manitoba, as a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Delmore C.W. Crewson, whose term has expired.
